Baseline (pre-training) measures estimated marginal means

Source: R/data.R
BASELINE_EMM.Rd

A list of emmGrid objects: NMR mass, lean mass, fat mass, VO\(_2\)max.

BASELINE_EMM

Format

An object of class list of length 7.

See also

BASELINE_STATS, emmeans

Examples

names(BASELINE_EMM) # available measures
#> [1] "NMR Weight"      "NMR Lean Mass"   "NMR Fat Mass"    "NMR % Lean"     
#> [5] "NMR % Fat"       "Absolute VO2max" "Relative VO2max"

str(BASELINE_EMM)
